    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus. This example is configured with the desirable G96 6-speed manual transaxle, offering crisp gate selection and precise heel-toe downshifts. The vehicle's longitudinal dynamics are supported by a factory-spec multi-link rear suspension and ventilated four-piston monobloc calipers. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a high-flow water pump to ensure thermal efficiency. While the Arctic Silver finish displays a light patina commensurate with an enjoyed driver, the chassis remains stiff and the throttle response is linear and immediate. This is a driver-focused 911 with a documented service history, ready for technical backroad duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
