    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a champ. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, clean, and totally ready for its next adventure! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a fun weekend getaway, this car still handles like a dream. It\u2019s got some great miles and memories on it, but it runs beautifully and is super reliable. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
