      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 987.2-generation Cayman S represents a pinnacle of mid-engine balance and mechanical purity. Powered by a 3.4L DFI flat-six, the 9A1 powerplant delivers linear torque through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, featuring MacPherson struts at all four corners and four-piston monobloc calipers for exceptional decelerative bite. Recent service includes a full cooling system refresh and a fresh set of high-performance tires. While showing signs of respectful use, the drivetrain is robust and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback lost in newer electric systems. A driver-focused machine ready for technical apexes.",
